<bibRefCitation author="Thorp, RW" journalOrPublisher="California Agriculture" pageId="22" pageNumber="53" pagination="20 - 23" title="Long-term studies to gauge effects of invading bees." volume="46" year="1992">Thorp et al. 1992</bibRefCitation>
